Hélène Rollès https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/H%C3%A9l%C3%A8ne_Roll%C3%A8s 0 Hélène Rollès (born 20 December 1966) is a French actress and singer, primarily known for her major role in the TV sitcom Helen and the boys (Hélène et les Garçons), alongside Sébastien Roch.
